snippet.title: Best VGM 1347 - Assassin's Creed III : The Tyranny of King Washington - Swift And Silent
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3 / Wii U / PC
Assassin's Creed III : The Tyranny of King Washington (2013)
Swift And Silent
Lorne Balfe
